directory containing files to run simulations for the tutorial

-------------------------------------------------------------------

First visualize the mesh with the associated bathymetry:

grid -fc7 GRID/venlag62.grd

shyplot GRID/venlag62.grd 

For the simulation in the tutorial you run the simulation as simply as

./shyfem venlag.str 

And for a simple postprocessing of surface fields:

shyplot -varid 2 -layer 1 venlag.hydro.shy  apn_venice_lagoon.str

shyplot -varid 11 -layer 1 venlag.ts.shy  apn_venice_lagoon.str

shyplot -varid 12 -layer 1 venlag.ts.shy  apn_venice_lagoon.str

To extract the gauge files in ASCII format run:

shyelab -split venlag.ext

-------------------------------------------------------------------

The tutorial can be found at the following address:

https://github.com/lucarpaia/shyfemcm-ismar/wiki/Three%E2%80%90dimensional-Venice-lagoon-simulation

-------------------------------------------------------------------
